&lt;p&gt;JOB TITLE: Pharmacy Dispenser&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SALARY: Negotiable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RESPONSIBLE TO: Pharmacy Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ACCOUNTABLE TO: Superintendent Pharmacist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;REPORTS TO: Pharmacy Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JOB SUMMARY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To support the efficient delivery of a hospital outpatient dispensing service, working with the pharmacy team to provide excellent patient care and safety.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To ensure that the patient is at the core of your performance and service delivery at all times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage dispensary workloads effectively and safely and ensure high standards of dispensing practices are delivered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Claire Morrison Email address claire.morrison@uhl-tr.nhs.uk Telephone number 0116 2541446&lt;/p&gt;
